At the end of the initiation plan it is expected that awareness, coordination and collaboration on the SDGs is enhanced, strengthening the enabling environment for the achievement of SDG-18 in particular. This will be achieved through: 
1.	Enhanced collaboration and coordination on the SDGs, SDG-18 in particular;
2.	Increased awareness of the national SDGs nationally and internationally, SDG-18 in particular.
